{"pageid":324391,"pagename":"Hazard Prevention","title":"Hazard Prevention","displaytitle":"Hazard Prevention","revid":14167135,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png"},{"name":"description","value":"Hazard Prevention is an elite combat achievement which requires the player to \"Kill the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil without it hitting anyone.\""}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-task\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"infobox-header\" colspan=\"5\"><b>Hazard Prevention</b>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-full-width-content\" colspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/w/File:Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Thermonuclear smoke devil.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png/150px-Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png?de858\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"186\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png/225px-Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png?de858 1.5x, /images/thumb/Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png/300px-Thermonuclear_smoke_devil.png?de858 2x\" data-file-width=\"1300\" data-file-height=\"1611\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Released\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/21_July\" title=\"21 July\">21 July</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Update:Combat Achievements\">Update</a>)\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Task\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">Kill the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil without it hitting anyone.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">Yes\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Area\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Smoke_Devil_Dungeon\" title=\"Smoke Devil Dungeon\">Smoke Devil Dungeon</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Reward\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">None\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Achievement_Diary\" title=\"Achievement Diary\">Diary</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Combat Achievements\">Combat Achievements</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Tier\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Elite\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Elite\">Elite</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hazard Prevention</b> is an <a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Elite\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Elite\">elite combat achievement</a> which requires the player to \"Kill the <a href=\"/w/Thermonuclear_Smoke_Devil\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thermonuclear Smoke Devil\">Thermonuclear Smoke Devil</a> without it hitting anyone.\"\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Hazard_Prevention?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Strategy\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Hazard_Prevention?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Strategy\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The achievement can be completed by hitting the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil and walking under it to avoid damage, then hitting it again, immediately teleporting out and running back to the cave. Setting NPC <a href=\"/w/Attack_options\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Attack options\">attack options</a> to right-click makes this easier.\n</p><p>Hits that land on the player as they are teleporting out do not invalidate the achievement, however they must be inside the room for the final hit or the task will not complete.\n</p><p>This task can be easily achieved alongside <a href=\"/w/Spec%27d_Out\" title=\"Spec&#39;d Out\">Spec'd Out</a> by teleporting to the <a href=\"/w/Ferox_Enclave\" title=\"Ferox Enclave\">Ferox Enclave</a>, a <a href=\"/w/Player-owned_house\" title=\"Player-owned house\">player-owned house</a> or <a href=\"/w/Nardah\" title=\"Nardah\">Nardah</a> and recharging <a href=\"/w/Special_attack_energy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Special attack energy\">special attack energy</a>.\n</p><p>A much more difficult method involves freezing the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil - preferably with <a href=\"/w/Ice_barrage\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ice barrage\">ice barrage</a> -trident set to long range, attack 4x from thermys max distance, before it's unfroze. Run out of  the cave, enter and refreeze from max distance again and attack 4x. Repeat until thermy dies, killing it before it becomes unbound. This approach requires a high magic level, damage-boosting gear.\n</p>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Combat Achievements\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Template:Combat Achievements\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Combat_Achievements\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Combat_Achievements?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Combat Achievements\">Combat Achievements</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group navbox-group-split\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title-hidden\" colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"></td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Ghommal\" title=\"Ghommal\"><img alt=\"Ghommal chathead.png: Chat head image of Ghommal\" src=\"/images/thumb/Ghommal_chathead.png/27px-Ghommal_chathead.png?39f54\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Ghommal_chathead.png/40px-Ghommal_chathead.png?39f54 1.5x, /images/thumb/Ghommal_chathead.png/53px-Ghommal_chathead.png?39f54 2x\" data-file-width=\"62\" data-file-height=\"81\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Ghommal\" title=\"Ghommal\">Ghommal</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Tiers</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/All_tasks\" title=\"Combat Achievements/All tasks\"><img alt=\"Combat achievements.png\" src=\"/images/Combat_achievements.png?b0e84\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/All_tasks\" title=\"Combat Achievements/All tasks\">All tasks</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Free-to-play\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Free-to-play\"><img alt=\"Free-to-play icon.png\" src=\"/images/Free-to-play_icon.png?628ce\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" data-file-width=\"16\" data-file-height=\"16\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Free-to-play\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Free-to-play\">Free-to-play</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Easy\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Easy\"><img alt=\"Combat Achievements - easy tier icon (small).png\" src=\"/images/Combat_Achievements_-_easy_tier_icon_%28small%29.png?904f9\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"22\"