_slayer_helmet\" title=\"Vampyric slayer helmet\"><img alt=\"Vampyric slayer helmet.png\" src=\"/images/Vampyric_slayer_helmet.png?fe40f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Vampyric_slayer_helmet\" title=\"Vampyric slayer helmet\">Vampyric</a> <small>(<a href=\"/w/Vampyric_slayer_helmet_(i)\" title=\"Vampyric slayer helmet (i)\">imbued</a>)</small></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Tzkal_slayer_helmet\" title=\"Tzkal slayer helmet\"><img alt=\"Tzkal slayer helmet.png\" src=\"/images/Tzkal_slayer_helmet.png?08f42\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Tzkal_slayer_helmet\" title=\"Tzkal slayer helmet\">TzKal</a> <small>(<a href=\"/w/Tzkal_slayer_helmet_(i)\" title=\"Tzkal slayer helmet (i)\">imbued</a>)</small></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐7nv7j\nCached time: 20220512005804\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.089 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.123 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 665/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 30353/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3336/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 853197/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   49.381      1 -total\n 84.35%   41.653      1 Template:Combat_Achievements\n 74.89%   36.982      2 Template:Navbox\n 15.49%    7.651      1 Template:Infobox_Task\n 13.77%    6.800      1 Template:Ctg\n  7.97%    3.938     25 Template:Plink\n  4.74%    2.340      6 Template:Ifincl\n  4.33%    2.138      1 Template:Parentitle\n  3.70%    1.828      1 Template:Chatl\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:324391-0!canonical and timestamp 20220512005804 and revision id 14167135. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{Infobox Task\n|name = Hazard Prevention\n|image = [[File:Thermonuclear smoke devil.png|150px]]\n|task = Kill the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil without it hitting anyone.\n|members = Yes\n|release = [[21 July]] [[2021]]\n|update = Combat Achievements\n|area = [[Smoke Devil Dungeon]]\n|reward = None\n|diary = [[Combat Achievements]]\n|tier = [[Combat Achievements/Elite|Elite]]\n}}\n\n'''Hazard Prevention''' is an [[Combat Achievements/Elite|elite combat achievement]] which requires the player to \"Kill the [[Thermonuclear Smoke Devil]] without it hitting anyone.\"\n\n==Strategy==\nThe achievement can be completed by hitting the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil and walking under it to avoid damage, then hitting it again, immediately teleporting out and running back to the cave. Setting NPC [[attack options]] to right-click makes this easier.\n\nHits that land on the player as they are teleporting out do not invalidate the achievement, however they must be inside the room for the final hit or the task will not complete.\n\nThis task can be easily achieved alongside [[Spec'd Out]] by teleporting to the [[Ferox Enclave]], a [[player-owned house]] or [[Nardah]] and recharging [[special attack energy]].\n\nA much more difficult method involves freezing the Thermonuclear Smoke Devil - preferably with [[ice barrage]] -trident set to long range, attack 4x from thermys max distance, before it's unfroze. Run out of  the cave, enter and refreeze from max distance again and attack 4x. Repeat until thermy dies, killing it before it becomes unbound. This approach requires a high magic level, damage-boosting gear.\n\n{{Combat Achievements}}"}